you hurt him too.

489
00:25:24,522 --> 00:25:25,732
Is that what happened?

490
00:25:29,194 --> 00:25:30,654
That's what happened, right?

491
00:25:39,579 --> 00:25:41,790
-No.
-Don't look at her.

492
00:25:42,457 --> 00:25:45,752
I don't care what she told you.
She is not your friend.

493
00:25:45,835 --> 00:25:48,213
-Yes, I am.
-Juliet, not another word.

494
00:25:49,047 --> 00:25:49,965
[sighs]

495
00:25:54,344 --> 00:25:56,346
I'm sorry. I have to.

496
00:25:59,474 --> 00:26:02,394
-It started when...
-It was Luisa! She just attacked me!

497
00:26:02,477 --> 00:26:05,814
Because he kept grabbing me!
You did this.

498
00:26:05,897 --> 00:26:08,775
He kept trying to hold my hand,
even when I told him to stop.

499
00:26:08,858 --> 00:26:10,110
Why didn't you tell me?

500
00:26:10,193 --> 00:26:13,822
Because Ollie said he wouldn't get in
trouble for just trying to hold my hand,

501
00:26:13,905 --> 00:26:15,907
but I wanted him to stop.

502
00:26:15,991 --> 00:26:19,661
-You're being a baby.
-No, she is not and you are in trouble.

503
00:26:20,829 --> 00:26:22,455
Ollie. Ollie...

504
00:26:23,206 --> 00:26:25,458
-Thank you. Take him to his room.
-Told you.

505
00:26:31,756 --> 00:26:32,757
<i>-Salam.</i>

506
00:26:32,841 --> 00:26:33,967
<i>We broke up.</i>

507
00:26:35,010 --> 00:26:36,094
<i>Ali and me.</i>

508
00:26:37,178 --> 00:26:38,805
-Oh?
-<i>You were right.</i>

509
00:26:38,888 --> 00:26:42,309
<i>I didn't want to marry him.
That was stupid.</i>

510
00:26:42,851 --> 00:26:44,185
<i>But I do want to come to New York.</i>

511
00:26:49,316 --> 00:26:50,775
You changed your mind, didn't you?

512
00:26:51,443 --> 00:26:52,652
It's, um...

513
00:26:53,653 --> 00:26:54,738
It's complicated.

514
00:26:56,114 --> 00:26:57,782
